  "content_html": "<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-4409eebd-9be9-41ef-ba36-1edb22625ac4\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-b6dbc5a5-4b64-4f81-9834-6323f616a916\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs15 se-ff-nanumgothic se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-18c01989-ce2f-4e5e-b245-194a3ec12822\" style=\"color:#0095e9;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>Story Boarding DAY 32</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-39a9be5f-9356-48c6-9596-a13f72fd0ceb\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs15 se-ff-nanumgothic se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-3a49aa73-ac33-418b-9ab3-dd832bfb0354\" style=\"color:#0095e9;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>​</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-afae29f6-c8ad-4540-af77-36d14b1ff631\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs15 se-ff-nanumgothic se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-49c135ef-29c6-41cd-ac84-444c2983628b\" style=\"color:#ff5f45;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>[본격적인 스토리보딩 작업]</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-2f87a4b4-9405-42ad-8f7f-c1efc02eeb00\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs15 se-ff-nanumgothic se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-5608b43b-7b27-4fe5-9c13-393b9ba969e6\" style=\"color:#ff5f45;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>이제 본격적으로 스토리보딩 작업에 들어갑니다. 지금까지는 자료나 개념에 대해 심도있게 생각했습니다. 물론 아직은 미흡한 부분이나 보강해야하는 사항이 있지만 앞으로 채워나가도록 하겠습니다. 이제부터는 하나하나 PPT 파일을 정리하도록 하겠습니다. 이제 시작입니다. 약 두달 뒤 나름 완벽한 (주)파파스컴퍼니 기획문서가 완성되기를 희망해 봅니다.</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-default\" id=\"SE-393ebd14-c635-47f8-8d64-be2e407d0dba\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-default\">\n<blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-4c9caacf-10a6-4582-a33c-46291f449d38\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs15 se-ff- se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-f8b7090d-7c17-4f16-ad0e-cd818d7a4e41\" style=\"color:#686868;\"><b>너무 소심하고 까다롭게 자신의 행동을 고민하지 말라 . 모든 인생은 실험이다 . 더많이 실험할수록 더나아진다 </b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-cite\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-96a12feb-85ce-46d7-8524-47668fc7fd37\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-\" id=\"SE-f59c8032-81ff-46aa-9f48-e911d9613a35\" style=\"\">랄프 왈도 에머슨</span></p></div>\n</blockquote>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-5e45858c-1e94-4759-8609-99ca7692b9d0\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-66b11c70-0dac-4c06-94ba-93727bd2d09b\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-32381bcc-3793-4b39-9b6b-160aa432ded4\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>​</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> \n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-048c42aa-22e7-4b72-baeb-0391079ab819\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-cd5dd87d-8966-4638-8d34-4643805dd2c2\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff- se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-29adeb1a-9aaa-4429-9638-95d582299d91\" style=\"color:#000000;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>Tip1. 위치, 배치에 따른 UI</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEX